sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Mind
    participant CX as Cortex
    participant RC as Recall
    participant HP as Hippocampus
    participant SL as Salience
    participant SY as Synapse

    C->>CX: search_memory
    CX->>RC: SearchQuery
    RC->>HP: Query matching memories
    HP-->>RC: MemoryRetrieved (candidates)
    RC->>SL: Request scores for candidates
    SL-->>RC: SalienceScored (scores)
    RC->>SY: Request associations for top candidates
    SY-->>RC: AssociationsFound (related memories)
    RC->>RC: Rank by score, include activated
    RC-->>CX: Ranked results
    CX-->>C: MCP tool response
